data.description: 2ND BITE FOR EVERYONE TO ENJOY!!! Adorable 2-Bed, 1-Bath single-level Bungalow in Portsmouth's Island Park with HUGE YARD in great shape!!!!  Maintenance Free exterior, vinyl sided with replacement windows and new roof!  Tons and Tons of space in rear yard!  Single car garage / workshop with plenty of off-street parking!  Peaks of the water and short walk to Beach / Park Ave Restaurants and Bars!  Great for AIR  BNB / short term rental!!  Property has cesspool and would need to be replaced within 1-Year... can be extended with a little finesse, and qualifies for low interest loan for install / free design plans!!!  Seller Financing available to qualified buyer!  PROPERTY SOLD AS-IS!!!
